HEADWORD: Water tiger
<hw>Wa"ter ti"ger</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>A diving,
or water, beetle, especially the larva of a water beetle. See
<xex>Illust.</xex> <it>b</it> of <er>Water beetle</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Water-tight</ent>⟦br⟧
